                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-0000008a4e6cf7-ff6a-44d4-b531-a0a03e98a87a" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\left[ 1\ \ \ \ 3\right] \left[ \begin{matrix}y &amp; x\\5 &amp; x\\\end{matrix}\right] =\left[ 12\ \ \ \ 4\right] \ ⇒\left[ \begin{matrix}y+15 &amp; 4x\\\end{matrix}\right] =\left[ \begin{matrix}12 &amp; 4\\\end{matrix}\right] \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000018a4e6cf7-ff6a-44d4-b531-a0a03e98a87a"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000008a4e6cf7-ff6a-44d4-b531-a0a03e98a87a {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000018a4e6cf7-ff6a-44d4-b531-a0a03e98a87a {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000054d7328b-54f8-44dc-8068-580f7aa06fcf" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000154d7328b-54f8-44dc-8068-580f7aa06fcf">A_&#169;vr, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(y+15=12⇒y=-3\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000154d7328b-54f8-44dc-8068-580f7aa06fcf">  </span><span class="pt-00000154d7328b-54f8-44dc-8068-580f7aa06fcf">Ges</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000154d7328b-54f8-44dc-8068-580f7aa06fcf"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(4x=4⇒x=1\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000054d7328b-54f8-44dc-8068-580f7aa06fcf {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000154d7328b-54f8-44dc-8068-580f7aa06fcf {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
