                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-0000004108f018-240c-4dcf-9b6e-7415cf50bb4a" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(x=rcosθ=3cos\frac{4π}{3}=-\frac{3}{2};\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000014108f018-240c-4dcf-9b6e-7415cf50bb4a"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000004108f018-240c-4dcf-9b6e-7415cf50bb4a {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000014108f018-240c-4dcf-9b6e-7415cf50bb4a {color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000031c4551d-673f-4e9e-b822-8e3404adb83d" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(y=rsinθ=3sin\ {\frac{4π}{3}}=-\frac{3\sqrt{3}}{2}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000131c4551d-673f-4e9e-b822-8e3404adb83d"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000031c4551d-673f-4e9e-b822-8e3404adb83d {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000131c4551d-673f-4e9e-b822-8e3404adb83d {font-family: ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
