                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000d09f1dea-f871-41ec-b6f9-a2658c3f76e0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(f\left(x\right)=sinx+cosx\ ;{f}^{{'}}\left(x\right)=cosx-sinx=0\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001d09f1dea-f871-41ec-b6f9-a2658c3f76e0"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000d09f1dea-f871-41ec-b6f9-a2658c3f76e0 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001d09f1dea-f871-41ec-b6f9-a2658c3f76e0 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000a270d024-1776-4f8b-aaaf-6129c200b687" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒sinx=cosx⇒tanx=1\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001a270d024-1776-4f8b-aaaf-6129c200b687"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴x=\frac{π}{4}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001a270d024-1776-4f8b-aaaf-6129c200b687"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000a270d024-1776-4f8b-aaaf-6129c200b687 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001a270d024-1776-4f8b-aaaf-6129c200b687 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
