                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-0000004812f42d-ee65-4549-aab0-be23ac174ba7" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(A=90^{\circ} ,\ \ B=30^{\circ} \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000014812f42d-ee65-4549-aab0-be23ac174ba7"> </span><span class="pt-0000014812f42d-ee65-4549-aab0-be23ac174ba7">n</span><span class="pt-0000014812f42d-ee65-4549-aab0-be23ac174ba7">‡</span><span class="pt-0000014812f42d-ee65-4549-aab0-be23ac174ba7">j,</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000014812f42d-ee65-4549-aab0-be23ac174ba7"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(C=180^{\circ} -A-B=180^{\circ} -90^{\circ} -30^{\circ} =60^{\circ} \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000014812f42d-ee65-4549-aab0-be23ac174ba7"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000004812f42d-ee65-4549-aab0-be23ac174ba7 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000014812f42d-ee65-4549-aab0-be23ac174ba7 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000093a1392e-1c37-427a-826f-1cc68b6292c0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000193a1392e-1c37-427a-826f-1cc68b6292c0">GLb, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\frac{a}{sin\ {A}}=\frac{b}{sin\ {B}}=\frac{c}{sin\ {C}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000293a1392e-1c37-427a-826f-1cc68b6292c0"> [sine </span><span class="pt-00000293a1392e-1c37-427a-826f-1cc68b6292c0">r</span><span class="pt-00000293a1392e-1c37-427a-826f-1cc68b6292c0">ule]</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000093a1392e-1c37-427a-826f-1cc68b6292c0 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000193a1392e-1c37-427a-826f-1cc68b6292c0 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-00000293a1392e-1c37-427a-826f-1cc68b6292c0 {font-family: Times New Roman;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000096055781-ac0f-4492-bc70-c997baefb113" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒\frac{BC}{sin\ {90^{\circ} }}=\frac{CA}{sin\ {30^{\circ} }}=\frac{AB}{sin\ {60^{\circ} }}⇒\frac{BC}{1}=\frac{CA}{\frac{1}{2}}=\frac{AB}{\frac{\sqrt{3}}{2}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000196055781-ac0f-4492-bc70-c997baefb113"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000096055781-ac0f-4492-bc70-c997baefb113 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000196055781-ac0f-4492-bc70-c997baefb113 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000701608b7-5a68-48a1-a1e2-c6352f4b7efb" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴\frac{BC}{2}=\frac{CA}{1}=\frac{AB}{\sqrt{3}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001701608b7-5a68-48a1-a1e2-c6352f4b7efb"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\left[ ∴BC\ :CA\ :AB=2\ :1\ :\sqrt{3}\right] \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001701608b7-5a68-48a1-a1e2-c6352f4b7efb"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000701608b7-5a68-48a1-a1e2-c6352f4b7efb {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001701608b7-5a68-48a1-a1e2-c6352f4b7efb {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
