                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000f4a4e7a5-c515-401a-bbb7-414836798519" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\underset{x→0}{lim}\ {\frac{{e}^{5x}+{e}^{-5x}-2}{{x}^{2}}};\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001f4a4e7a5-c515-401a-bbb7-414836798519"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\((\frac{0}{0}\ \text{আকার})\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001f4a4e7a5-c515-401a-bbb7-414836798519">  </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000f4a4e7a5-c515-401a-bbb7-414836798519 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001f4a4e7a5-c515-401a-bbb7-414836798519 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000d8257a87-1a05-4f7e-8e63-d589e9f2c834" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=\underset{x→0}{lim}\ {\frac{{5e}^{5x}-5{e}^{-5x}}{2{x}^{\ }}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001d8257a87-1a05-4f7e-8e63-d589e9f2c834"> [</span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({L}^{{'}}H\widehat {o}pita{l}^{{'}}s\ rule;\frac{0}{0}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001d8257a87-1a05-4f7e-8e63-d589e9f2c834"> </span><span class="pt-000001d8257a87-1a05-4f7e-8e63-d589e9f2c834">AvK</span><span class="pt-000001d8257a87-1a05-4f7e-8e63-d589e9f2c834">…</span><span class="pt-000001d8257a87-1a05-4f7e-8e63-d589e9f2c834">wZ</span><span class="pt-000001d8257a87-1a05-4f7e-8e63-d589e9f2c834">]</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000d8257a87-1a05-4f7e-8e63-d589e9f2c834 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001d8257a87-1a05-4f7e-8e63-d589e9f2c834 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000a59f7a25-8138-446e-98be-d72ad4adcdff" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=\underset{x→0}{lim}\ {\frac{{25e}^{5x}+\ 25{e}^{-5x}}{2}};\left[ ≠\frac{0}{0}\text{আকৃতি}\right] \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001a59f7a25-8138-446e-98be-d72ad4adcdff"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=\frac{25+25}{2}=25\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000a59f7a25-8138-446e-98be-d72ad4adcdff {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001a59f7a25-8138-446e-98be-d72ad4adcdff {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
