                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000ce3b7d7e-4d33-49d7-8c13-a822add8ec94" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001ce3b7d7e-4d33-49d7-8c13-a822add8ec94"><img src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 0.6926914in;height: 0.7197802in;" alt="Picture 1" /></span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000ce3b7d7e-4d33-49d7-8c13-a822add8ec94 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001ce3b7d7e-4d33-49d7-8c13-a822add8ec94 {color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000f820a06e-648b-4218-9bce-ddf2b6f64e3c" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({tan}^{-1}\ {\frac{2}{3}}+{cos}^{-1}\ {\frac{2}{\sqrt{13}}}={tan}^{-1}\ {\frac{2}{3}}+{tan}^{-1}\ {\frac{3}{2}}\ ={tan}^{-1}\ {\frac{2}{3}}+{cot}^{-1}\ {\frac{2}{3}}=\frac{π}{2}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001f820a06e-648b-4218-9bce-ddf2b6f64e3c"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000f820a06e-648b-4218-9bce-ddf2b6f64e3c {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001f820a06e-648b-4218-9bce-ddf2b6f64e3c {font-family: Times New Roman;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
