                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p class="pt-00000053f1cbea-4e6a-4bf1-b9a2-ada2aececc79" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\int \frac{tanx}{ln|cosx|}dx=?\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000153f1cbea-4e6a-4bf1-b9a2-ada2aececc79"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000053f1cbea-4e6a-4bf1-b9a2-ada2aececc79 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000153f1cbea-4e6a-4bf1-b9a2-ada2aececc79 {font-family: Times New Roman;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p>
