                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-0000006a35636b-b498-42dc-b996-a57a8438fef3" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\int \frac{tanx}{ln|cosx|}dx\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000016a35636b-b498-42dc-b996-a57a8438fef3"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000006a35636b-b498-42dc-b996-a57a8438fef3 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000016a35636b-b498-42dc-b996-a57a8438fef3 {font-family: Times New Roman;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000c04823c5-01fd-4681-898f-8f8fdf8e7767" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(Let,ln\ {\left| cosx\right| }=z⇒\frac{1}{cosx}\left(-sinx\right)dx=dz⇒-tanx\ dx=dz\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001c04823c5-01fd-4681-898f-8f8fdf8e7767"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000c04823c5-01fd-4681-898f-8f8fdf8e7767 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001c04823c5-01fd-4681-898f-8f8fdf8e7767 {font-family: Times New Roman;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000061f330a7-b514-4684-bc23-5164703012f3" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(Now,\ \int \frac{tanx\ dx}{ln|cosx|}=\int \frac{-dz}{z}=-ln\ {\left| z\right| }+c=-ln\ {\left(ln\ {\left| cosx\right| }\right)}+c\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000161f330a7-b514-4684-bc23-5164703012f3"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000061f330a7-b514-4684-bc23-5164703012f3 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000161f330a7-b514-4684-bc23-5164703012f3 {font-family: Times New Roman;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 9 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p class="pt-000000a4b94f56-509e-4f42-ba4b-97a207a78920" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\int {x}^{n}\ dx=\frac{{x}^{n+1}}{n+1}+c\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001a4b94f56-509e-4f42-ba4b-97a207a78920"> m~&#206;wU c&#214;‡hvR&#168; n‡e bv hLb</span><span class="pt-000001a4b94f56-509e-4f42-ba4b-97a207a78920">-</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001a4b94f56-509e-4f42-ba4b-97a207a78920"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000a4b94f56-509e-4f42-ba4b-97a207a78920 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001a4b94f56-509e-4f42-ba4b-97a207a78920 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row questionOptions">
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                                        <div class="input-group" style="align-items: center;">
                                            <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                                <span class="input-group-text">A</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="input-group-append questionTable">
                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p class="pt-0000008dc366f6-8f5d-47d3-ac6e-120421df1e9f" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(n=1\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000018dc366f6-8f5d-47d3-ac6e-120421df1e9f"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000008dc366f6-8f5d-47d3-ac6e-120421df1e9f {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000018dc366f6-8f5d-47d3-ac6e-120421df1e9f {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                                        <div class="input-group" style="align-items: center;">
                                            <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                                <span class="input-group-text">B</span>
