                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-00000029d1a78d-4471-49ab-8831-6d1fcb10c0e0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(7x+5y+k=0\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000129d1a78d-4471-49ab-8831-6d1fcb10c0e0">,  </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\left(2,-3\right)\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000129d1a78d-4471-49ab-8831-6d1fcb10c0e0"> </span><span class="pt-00000129d1a78d-4471-49ab-8831-6d1fcb10c0e0">we</span><span class="pt-00000129d1a78d-4471-49ab-8831-6d1fcb10c0e0">›</span><span class="pt-00000129d1a78d-4471-49ab-8831-6d1fcb10c0e0">`yMvgx e</span><span class="pt-00000129d1a78d-4471-49ab-8831-6d1fcb10c0e0">‡</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000129d1a78d-4471-49ab-8831-6d1fcb10c0e0">j, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(7\times 2+5\times \left(-3\right)+k=0⇒k=1\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000029d1a78d-4471-49ab-8831-6d1fcb10c0e0 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000129d1a78d-4471-49ab-8831-6d1fcb10c0e0 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000002730ffaa-2371-4360-977e-ac7d81484656" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴7x+5y+1=0\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000012730ffaa-2371-4360-977e-ac7d81484656"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000002730ffaa-2371-4360-977e-ac7d81484656 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000012730ffaa-2371-4360-977e-ac7d81484656 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></