                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-00000067c227a2-1894-491b-8346-a5e2d519afcf" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\int_{0}^{1} \frac{ln\ {\left(x+1\right)}}{\left(x+1\right)}dx\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000167c227a2-1894-491b-8346-a5e2d519afcf">; </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000067c227a2-1894-491b-8346-a5e2d519afcf {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000167c227a2-1894-491b-8346-a5e2d519afcf {font-family: Times New Roman;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000cb72d94e-9847-49ac-9716-6a7e3a1ae755" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001cb72d94e-9847-49ac-9716-6a7e3a1ae755">[</span><span class="pt-000002cb72d94e-9847-49ac-9716-6a7e3a1ae755">awi,</span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(ln\ {(x+1)}=z;\frac{1}{\left(x+1\right)}dx=dz;\ \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001cb72d94e-9847-49ac-9716-6a7e3a1ae755">] </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001cb72d94e-9847-49ac-9716-6a7e3a1ae755"><span>            </span></span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000cb72d94e-9847-49ac-9716-6a7e3a1ae755 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001cb72d94e-9847-49ac-9716-6a7e3a1ae755 {font-family: Times New Roman;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-000002cb72d94e-9847-49ac-9716-6a7e3a1ae755 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000ffc551cd-2501-4ba8-8011-54489380224b" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><a id="_Hlk166164457" class="pt-000001ffc551cd-2501-4ba8-8011-54489380224b"></a><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴\int_{0}^{ln\ {2}} z\ dz\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000002ffc551cd-2501-4ba8-8011-54489380224b"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(={\left[ \frac{{z}^{2}}{2}\right] }_{0}^{ln\ {2}}=\frac{1}{2}\left[ {\left(ln\ {2}\right)}^{2}-{0}^{2}\right] \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000002ffc551cd-2501-4ba8-8011-54489380224b">   </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000ffc551cd-2501-4ba8-8011-54489380224b {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}a.pt-000001ffc551cd-2501-4ba8-8011-54489380224b {text-decoration: none;}span.pt-000002ffc551cd-2501-4ba8-8011-54489380224b {font-family: Times New Roman;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000eef16c52-bff7-4026-9e2f-cd3d83b70808" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=\frac{1}{2}{\left(ln\ {2}\right)}^{2}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001eef16c52-bff7-4026-9e2f-cd3d83b70808"> </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001eef16c52-bff7-4026-9e2f-cd3d83b70808"><span>            </span></span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000eef16c52-bff7-4026-9e2f-cd3d83b70808 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001eef16c52-bff7-4026-9e2f-cd3d83b70808 {font-family: Times New Roman;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000001878a159-f46a-4de3-8329-564a6e8c8ea5" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000011878a159-f46a-4de3-8329-564a6e8c8ea5">weK&#237;:</span><a id="_Hlk167786156" class="pt-0000021878a159-f46a-4de3-8329-564a6e8c8ea5"></a><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000031878a159-f46a-4de3-8329-564a6e8c8ea5"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\int_{0}^{1} \frac{ln\ {\left(x+1\right)}}{x+1}dx=\int_{0}^{1} ln\ {\left(x+1\right)}d\left(ln\ {\left(x+1\right)}\right)\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000001878a159-f46a-4de3-8329-564a6e8c8ea5 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000011878a159-f46a-4de3-8329-564a6e8c8ea5 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}a.pt-0000021878a159-f46a-4de3-8329-564a6e8c8ea5 {text-decoration: none;}span.pt-0000031878a159-f46a-4de3-8329-564a6e8c8ea5 {font-family: SolaimanLipi;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000c9e558cf-56fe-4223-adfa-7d36aa68775b" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(={\left[ \frac{{\left\{ln\ {\left(x+1\right)}\right\}}^{1+1}}{1+1}\right] }_{0}^{1}=\frac{1}{2}{\left(ln\ {2}\right)}^{2}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001c9e558cf-56fe-4223-adfa-7d36aa68775b"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000c9e558cf-56fe-4223-adfa-7d36aa68775b {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001c9e558cf-56fe-4223-adfa-7d36aa68775b {font-family: SolaimanLipi;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
