                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000a308781a-3923-4961-9670-5ad34ad24445" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001a308781a-3923-4961-9670-5ad34ad24445">kZ&#169;g‡Z, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\sqrt{{\left(x+1\right)}^{2}+{\left(y-0\right)}^{2}}=\frac{\left| x-1\right| }{\sqrt{{1}^{2}+{0}^{2}}}\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000a308781a-3923-4961-9670-5ad34ad24445 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001a308781a-3923-4961-9670-5ad34ad24445 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000034223ebb-b6d4-41a7-aa34-e2829ac49c24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒{\left(x+1\right)}^{2}+{y}^{2}={\left(x-1\right)}^{2}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000134223ebb-b6d4-41a7-aa34-e2829ac49c24"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000034223ebb-b6d4-41a7-aa34-e2829ac49c24 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000134223ebb-b6d4-41a7-aa34-e2829ac49c24 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000c0d34df2-ca66-456c-84a4-36a7b172f0f8" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒{y}^{2}=-4x⇒{y}^{2}+4x=0\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001c0d34df2-ca66-456c-84a4-36a7b172f0f8"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000c0d34df2-ca66-456c-84a4-36a7b172f0f8 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001c0d34df2-ca66-456c-84a4-36a7b172f0f8 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: b