                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000271fb615-47a1-4a04-a7b0-2d85bab8f34a" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(y={x}^{-2}ln\ {x}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001271fb615-47a1-4a04-a7b0-2d85bab8f34a"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000271fb615-47a1-4a04-a7b0-2d85bab8f34a {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001271fb615-47a1-4a04-a7b0-2d85bab8f34a {font-family: Times New Roman;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000a600a3dd-6510-4c34-be43-8dbce991311f" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒\frac{dy}{dx}={x}^{-2}⋅\frac{1}{x}+(ln\ {x)\left(-2\right){x}^{-3}}={x}^{-3}-2{x}^{-3}ln\ {x}⇒\frac{dy}{dx}={x}^{-3}\left(1-2ln\ {x}\right)\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001a600a3dd-6510-4c34-be43-8dbce991311f"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000a600a3dd-6510-4c34-be43-8dbce991311f {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001a600a3dd-6510-4c34-be43-8dbce991311f {font-family: Times New Roman;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000652d5ace-9133-4296-bda8-80fcdfe4f4d5" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒\frac{{d}^{2}y}{d{x}^{2}}={x}^{-3}\left(0-\frac{2}{x}\right)+\left(1-2ln\ {x}\right)\left(-3\right){x}^{-4}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001652d5ace-9133-4296-bda8-80fcdfe4f4d5"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000652d5ace-9133-4296-bda8-80fcdfe4f4d5 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;