                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000ce947337-37f6-4820-bd04-ab05f6a475db" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001ce947337-37f6-4820-bd04-ab05f6a475db">we</span><span class="pt-000001ce947337-37f6-4820-bd04-ab05f6a475db">›</span><span class="pt-000001ce947337-37f6-4820-bd04-ab05f6a475db">`y&#206;q mg</span><span class="pt-000001ce947337-37f6-4820-bd04-ab05f6a475db">‡</span><span class="pt-000001ce947337-37f6-4820-bd04-ab05f6a475db">iL nevi kZ&#169; n</span><span class="pt-000001ce947337-37f6-4820-bd04-ab05f6a475db">‡”</span><span class="pt-000001ce947337-37f6-4820-bd04-ab05f6a475db">Q</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001ce947337-37f6-4820-bd04-ab05f6a475db">, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\frac{a-0}{0-b}=\frac{0-1}{b-1}\ \ \Rightarrow\ ab-a=b∴a+b=ab\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000ce947337-37f6-4820-bd04-ab05f6a475db {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001ce947337-37f6-4820-bd04-ab05f6a475db {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
