                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000b5dfe06e-864e-41a0-b389-a538f7ce8b63" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\int \frac{{x}^{2}-x+1}{{x}^{3}+1}dx=\int \frac{\left({x}^{2}-x+1\right)}{\left(x+1\right)\left({x}^{2}-x+1\right)}dx\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001b5dfe06e-864e-41a0-b389-a538f7ce8b63"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000b5dfe06e-864e-41a0-b389-a538f7ce8b63 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001b5dfe06e-864e-41a0-b389-a538f7ce8b63 {color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000003294a6a7-15a7-4565-bfd2-059b38667204" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=\int \frac{dx}{x+1}=ln\ {\left| x+1\right| }+c\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000013294a6a7-15a7-4565-bfd2-059b38667204"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000003294a6a7-15a7-4565-bfd2-059b38667204 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000013294a6a7-15a7-4565-bfd2-059b38667204 {font-family: Times New Roman;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
