                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-0000001fc7bcc4-0c6f-4790-b903-67fbeb78ac5e" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000011fc7bcc4-0c6f-4790-b903-67fbeb78ac5e"><img src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 2.2343645in;height: 1.475in;" alt="Picture 1" /></span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000001fc7bcc4-0c6f-4790-b903-67fbeb78ac5e {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000011fc7bcc4-0c6f-4790-b903-67fbeb78ac5e {color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000002348011f-f420-4421-89ca-f48e056a75bc" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000012348011f-f420-4421-89ca-f48e056a75bc"> wb</span><span class="pt-0000012348011f-f420-4421-89ca-f48e056a75bc">‡</span><span class="pt-0000012348011f-f420-4421-89ca-f48e056a75bc">Y</span><span class="pt-0000012348011f-f420-4421-89ca-f48e056a75bc">&#169;</span><span class="pt-0000012348011f-f420-4421-89ca-f48e056a75bc">q jw</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000012348011f-f420-4421-89ca-f48e056a75bc">&#228; </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=\sqrt{{8}^{2}+{4}^{2}+2\times 8\times 4\times cos\ {120^{\circ} }}\ =\sqrt{48}=4\sqrt{3}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000012348011f-f420-4421-89ca-f48e056a75bc"> </span><span class="pt-0000012348011f-f420-4421-89ca-f48e056a75bc">GKK</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000002348011f-f420-4421-89ca-f48e056a75bc {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000012348011f-f420-4421-89ca-f48e056a75bc {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000d5f519a7-78bb-4846-82