                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-0000002bde3233-b3ab-472d-8a6f-cfe76bd957ee" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(p-i=pi-1\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000012bde3233-b3ab-472d-8a6f-cfe76bd957ee">, ev&#175;&#205;e </span><span class="pt-0000012bde3233-b3ab-472d-8a6f-cfe76bd957ee">As</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000012bde3233-b3ab-472d-8a6f-cfe76bd957ee">‡ki mnM mgxK…Z K‡i cvB, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(p=-1\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000002bde3233-b3ab-472d-8a6f-cfe76bd957ee {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000012bde3233-b3ab-472d-8a6f-cfe76bd957ee {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
