                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000c05ce910-742a-45d0-aa55-10cf0caea2e6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(cos\ {2θ}-cos\ {3θ}=0\ ⇒2sin\ {\frac{5θ}{2}sin\ {\frac{θ}{2}=0}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001c05ce910-742a-45d0-aa55-10cf0caea2e6"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000c05ce910-742a-45d0-aa55-10cf0caea2e6 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001c05ce910-742a-45d0-aa55-10cf0caea2e6 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000b22e2292-d32c-4174-8556-d49fe79ed102" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(sin\frac{5θ}{2}=0\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001b22e2292-d32c-4174-8556-d49fe79ed102"> n</span><span class="pt-000001b22e2292-d32c-4174-8556-d49fe79ed102">‡</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001b22e2292-d32c-4174-8556-d49fe79ed102">j, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\frac{5θ}{2}=nπ⇒θ=\frac{2nπ}{5}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001b22e2292-d32c-4174-8556-d49fe79ed102">; </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000b22e2292-d32c-4174-8556-d49fe79ed102 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001b22e2292-d32c-4174-8556-d49fe79ed102 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000007460356f-cef0-4292-b762-06e7a22ab143" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(sin\ {\frac{θ}{2}}=0\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000017460356f-cef0-4292