                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-0000007390356f-6d47-438c-b622-817f0e4d8134" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(sin\ {θ}-2=cos\ {2θ}=1-2\ si{n}^{2}θ\ \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000017390356f-6d47-438c-b622-817f0e4d8134"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000007390356f-6d47-438c-b622-817f0e4d8134 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000017390356f-6d47-438c-b622-817f0e4d8134 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000c8a0dea6-a4e7-445f-8d9a-4e1427201dd9" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒2{sin}^{2}\ {θ}+sin\ {θ}-3=0\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001c8a0dea6-a4e7-445f-8d9a-4e1427201dd9"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000c8a0dea6-a4e7-445f-8d9a-4e1427201dd9 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001c8a0dea6-a4e7-445f-8d9a-4e1427201dd9 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000008ff97433-4f6b-4298-af02-806194488c79" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒2{sin}^{2}\ {θ}+3sin\ {θ}-2sin\ {θ}-3=0\ \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000018ff97433-4f6b-4298-af02-806194488c79"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000008ff97433-4f6b-4298-af02-806194488c79 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000018ff97433-4f6b-4298-af02-806194488c79 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p cla