                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000d1c38a60-ee2f-4fad-b78d-16624a82a6da" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(tan\ {90^{\circ} }=\frac{2Psin\ {α}}{P\ +\ \ 2Pcos\ {α}}=\frac{1}{0}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001d1c38a60-ee2f-4fad-b78d-16624a82a6da"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000d1c38a60-ee2f-4fad-b78d-16624a82a6da {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001d1c38a60-ee2f-4fad-b78d-16624a82a6da {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000868195d0-0012-462b-9f9d-e0190fd45a76" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒P+2Pcos\ {α}=0\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001868195d0-0012-462b-9f9d-e0190fd45a76"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒cos\ {α}=-\frac{1}{2}∴α=120^{\circ} \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001868195d0-0012-462b-9f9d-e0190fd45a76"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000868195d0-0012-462b-9f9d-e0190fd45a76 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001868195d0-0012-462b-9f9d-e0190fd45a76 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000a1f45105-7eb4-48ea-9e67-c55154ed54a2" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001a1f45105-7eb4-48ea-9e67-c55154ed54a2"><img src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 0.90427274in;height: 0.8343559in;" alt="Picture 1" /></span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000a1f45105-7eb4-48ea-9e67-c55154ed54a2 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001a1f45105-7eb4-48ea-9e67-c55154ed54a2 {color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000059aae0d8-bafc-4205-a399-b053cd7dec84" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-00000159aae0d8-bafc-4205-a399-b053cd7dec84">weK&#237;:</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000259aae0d8-bafc-4205-a399-b053cd7dec84"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(sinθ=\frac{P}{2P}∴θ={sin}^{-1}\ {\left(\frac{1}{2}\right)}=30^{\circ} \) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000059aae0d8-bafc-4205-a399-b053cd7dec84 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000159aae0d8-bafc-4205-a399-b053cd7dec84 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-00000259aae0d8-bafc-4205-a399-b053cd7dec84 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000923be21a-ebbd-4fe9-90e2-3d8654c78a63" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴α=90^{\circ} +θ=90^{\circ} +30^{\circ} =120^{\circ} \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001923be21a-ebbd-4fe9-90e2-3d8654c78a63"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000923be21a-ebbd-4fe9-90e2-3d8654c78a63 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001923be21a-ebbd-4fe9-90e2-3d8654c78a63 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
