                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000c9942ff2-517a-46d3-b1d4-d22fa570f9d4" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(tan\ {20^{\circ} }tan\ {40^{\circ} }tan\ {80^{\circ} }\ =tan\ {20^{\circ} }tan\ {\left(60^{\circ} -20^{\circ} \right)}tan\ {\left(60^{\circ} +20^{\circ} \right)}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001c9942ff2-517a-46d3-b1d4-d22fa570f9d4">  </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000c9942ff2-517a-46d3-b1d4-d22fa570f9d4 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001c9942ff2-517a-46d3-b1d4-d22fa570f9d4 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000eed0030c-b8e2-48d4-8e53-42aac25feffc" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=tan\ {20^{\circ} }.\frac{\sqrt{3}-tan20^{\circ} }{1+\sqrt{3}tan20^{\circ} }.\frac{\sqrt{3}+tan20^{\circ} }{1-\sqrt{3}tan20^{\circ} }\ =tan20^{\circ} \frac{3-ta{n}^{2}20^{\circ} }{1-3ta{n}^{2}20^{\circ} }\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001eed0030c-b8e2-48d4-8e53-42aac25feffc"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000eed0030c-b8e2-48d4-8e53-42aac25feffc {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001eed0030c-b8e2-48d4-8e53-42aac25feffc {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000258771e3-8439-45d8-9201-ef135b128e9d" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=\frac{3tan20^{\circ} -{tan}^{3}\ {20^{\circ} }}{1-3{tan}^{2}\ {20^{\circ} }}=tan\ {\left(3⋅20^{\circ} \right)}=tan\ {60^{\circ} }=\sqrt{3}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" c