                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-0000003a413e5a-08a0-450d-8f05-e5e03044465e" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(cotθ=\frac{6}{5}\ ∴\frac{sinθ\left(5-3cotθ\right)}{sinθ\left(1+2cotθ\right)}=\frac{5-3.\ \frac{6}{5}\ }{1+2.\frac{6}{5}}=\frac{25-18}{5+12}=\frac{7}{17}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000013a413e5a-08a0-450d-8f05-e5e03044465e"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000003a413e5a-08a0-450d-8f05-e5e03044465e {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000013a413e5a-08a0-450d-8f05-e5e03044465e {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
