                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000f901ca4f-7e19-4275-98cc-ebb955139fc7" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(cos\ {θ}+sec\ {θ}=2\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001f901ca4f-7e19-4275-98cc-ebb955139fc7"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒cos\ {θ}+\frac{1}{cos\ {θ}}=2\ \) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000f901ca4f-7e19-4275-98cc-ebb955139fc7 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001f901ca4f-7e19-4275-98cc-ebb955139fc7 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000009a89aea7-5369-486c-8279-9925cce4ea0b" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒{cos}^{2}\ {θ}-2cos\ {θ}+1=0\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000019a89aea7-5369-486c-8279-9925cce4ea0b"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000009a89aea7-5369-486c-8279-9925cce4ea0b {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000019a89aea7-5369-486c-8279-9925cce4ea0b {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000ae02e16c-3784-4d0b-b3a9-8cdfc8d8118a" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒{\left(cos\ {θ}-1\right)}^{2}=0\ ⇒cos\ {θ}=1\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001ae02e16c-3784-4d0b-b3a9-8cdfc8d8118a"> </span><span class="pt-000001ae02e16c-3784-4d0b-b3a9-8cdfc8d8118a">Ges</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001ae02e16c-3784-4d0b-b3a9-8cdfc8d8118a"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(sec\ {θ}=1\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000ae02e16c-3784-4d0b-b3a9-8cdfc8d8118a {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001ae02e16c-3784-4d0b-b3a9-8cdfc8d8118a {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000abea335b-38a9-4f8e-ad59-60c4580a6497" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴{cos}^{10}\ {θ}+{sec}^{9}\ {θ}={1}^{10}+{1}^{9}=1+1=2\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001abea335b-38a9-4f8e-ad59-60c4580a6497"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000abea335b-38a9-4f8e-ad59-60c4580a6497 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001abea335b-38a9-4f8e-ad59-60c4580a6497 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
