                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-00000065d9f2a2-e4e7-458c-a587-fd3fa80e4a6d" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-00000165d9f2a2-e4e7-458c-a587-fd3fa80e4a6d"><img src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 1.3618056in;height: 1.1041666in;" alt="Picture 1" /></span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000065d9f2a2-e4e7-458c-a587-fd3fa80e4a6d {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000165d9f2a2-e4e7-458c-a587-fd3fa80e4a6d {color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000ebf72acb-c01b-4d68-8687-9e9d491cdfbd" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴\ \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001ebf72acb-c01b-4d68-8687-9e9d491cdfbd">†&#182;&#206;dj </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=\int_{0}^{4} {\left[ 2\sqrt{x}-x\right] }_{\ }^{\ }dx\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000ebf72acb-c01b-4d68-8687-9e9d491cdfbd {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001ebf72acb-c01b-4d68-8687-9e9d491cdfbd {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000007169bebf-2c7f-40b4-b148-3e079b8617a7" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=2\times \frac{2}{3}\times {\left[ {x}^{\frac{3}{2}}\right] }_{0}^{4}-\frac{1}{2}{\left[ {x}^{2}\right] }_{0\ }^{4}=\frac{4}{3}\times {4}^{\frac{3}{2}}-\frac{1}{2}\times {4}^{2}\ =\frac{4}{3}\times 8-8\ \ \ =\frac{8}{3}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000017169bebf-2c7f-40b4-b148-3e079b8617a7">  </span><span class="pt-0000017169bebf-2c7f-40b4-b148-3e079b8617a7">eM&#169; GKK</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000007169bebf-2c7f-40b4-b148-3e079b8617a7 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000017169bebf-2c7f-40b4-b148-3e079b8617a7 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000a303dc86-1cb7-4441-88a7-818fb1bfb669" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001a303dc86-1cb7-4441-88a7-818fb1bfb669">Shortcut:</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000002a303dc86-1cb7-4441-88a7-818fb1bfb669"> </span><span class="pt-000002a303dc86-1cb7-4441-88a7-818fb1bfb669">†</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000002a303dc86-1cb7-4441-88a7-818fb1bfb669">&#182;&#206;dj </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=\frac{8{a}^{2}}{3{m}^{3}}=\frac{8\times {1}^{2}}{3\times {1}^{3}\ }=\frac{8}{3}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000002a303dc86-1cb7-4441-88a7-818fb1bfb669"> </span><span class="pt-000002a303dc86-1cb7-4441-88a7-818fb1bfb669">eM&#169; GKK</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000a303dc86-1cb7-4441-88a7-818fb1bfb669 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001a303dc86-1cb7-4441-88a7-818fb1bfb669 {font-family: Times New Roman;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-000002a303dc86-1cb7-4441-88a7-818fb1bfb669 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
