                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000902132db-d1fe-448f-8a62-7ff523c6a1b3" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001902132db-d1fe-448f-8a62-7ff523c6a1b3">ধরি</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001902132db-d1fe-448f-8a62-7ff523c6a1b3">, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(z=3x+1⇒dz=3dx\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001902132db-d1fe-448f-8a62-7ff523c6a1b3">  ;  </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000902132db-d1fe-448f-8a62-7ff523c6a1b3 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001902132db-d1fe-448f-8a62-7ff523c6a1b3 {font-family: SolaimanLipi;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000003a83ac41-ad54-42da-85ca-8dcdcd5eed65" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000013a83ac41-ad54-42da-85ca-8dcdcd5eed65">যখন</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000013a83ac41-ad54-42da-85ca-8dcdcd5eed65"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(x=0,\ z=1\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000013a83ac41-ad54-42da-85ca-8dcdcd5eed65"> </span><span class="pt-0000013a83ac41-ad54-42da-85ca-8dcdcd5eed65">এবং</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000013a83ac41-ad54-42da-85ca-8dcdcd5eed65"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(x=1,\ \ z=4\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000013a83ac41-ad54-42da-85ca-8dcdcd5eed65">  </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000003a83ac41-ad54-42da-85ca-8dcdcd5eed65 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000013a83ac41-ad54-42da-85ca-8dcdcd5eed65 {font-family: SolaimanLipi;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000