                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000430fb9a3-0306-4522-9e7c-00618c6dd88a" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(cos\ {\theta}=\frac{12}{13};tan\ {\theta}=\ ±\frac{5}{12}\ \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001430fb9a3-0306-4522-9e7c-00618c6dd88a"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000430fb9a3-0306-4522-9e7c-00618c6dd88a {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001430fb9a3-0306-4522-9e7c-00618c6dd88a {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000077e019a4-839b-4653-9491-14a597521142" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴tan\ {2\theta}\ =\frac{2tan\ {\theta}}{1-{tan}^{2}\ {\theta}}=±\frac{2.\frac{5}{12}}{1-{\left(\frac{5}{12}\right)}^{2}}=±\frac{120}{119}\ \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000177e019a4-839b-4653-9491-14a597521142"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000077e019a4-839b-4653-9491-14a597521142 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000177e019a4-839b-4653-9491-14a597521142 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
